component.itemContent_html:
Mavinex provides optimal solutions from the master plan to the detailed farm design, and advises investors to apply advanced breeding technologies in accordance with the development trend, in accordance with breeding standards, ensure efficient and sustainable financial investment.

Currently Mavinex is supporting, consulting and supplying equipment for pig, chicken and duck farms throughout the country and cities such as Thai Binh, Phu Tho, Bac Ninh, Hoa Binh, Hung Yen and Bac Giang. , Hai Duong, Quang Ninh, Thanh Hoa, Nghe An, Hau Giang ... The projects are praised and appreciated by investors and partners.
